{"tid":378241,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港旗設計比賽2017","createTime":"2017-08-28T10:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T13:02:04.000Z","uid":135408,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e9f11d84519cc46e1a27228eb8990911cca5d4","tid":378241,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"最近睇到有個Facebook Post講關於屬於香港既花 又諗起咁多年用既洋紫荊香港旗其實美感就差左啲 所以小弟就想係度開返個2017香港旗設計比賽 比大家發揮下創意咁 希望大家踴躍啲參加，大家旨在交流下<br />\n<br />\n希望大家post圖都可以講下設計靈感<br />\n<br />\n小弟先獻上自己既作品<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/183712_ce1cc0fc66e831a4d19dba3b53ba8ba0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F183712_ce1cc0fc66e831a4d19dba3b53ba8ba0.png&h=385e2406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n靈感黎自英國國旗同中國五星旗 代表中國及英國皆對香港行使主權 寄望後人反省歷史 對香港作出更大貢獻 以及香港龍獅旗代表香港徽"},{"pid":"57941bf9cbcc69b0d419371df4c4d49d4248f5af","tid":378241,"uid":34525,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:45:19.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"146114f9cd6605a177956724178cbe2d52a4172d","tid":378241,"uid":135408,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:47:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9</blockquote><br />\n睇黎你對現實都幾大怨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3165cf6d703860a4d9e3993d430e5c15735decad","tid":378241,"uid":21924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:51:35.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"c2d96298ad237ef9f4dd9e55af98224870aab0cd","tid":378241,"uid":17866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:55:28.000Z","msg":"On 9"},{"pid":"0e8ef079d372bb6fe078e8b58347df570e89db65","tid":378241,"uid":7033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:56:05.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"a61e6c7e0c6428f7a04a2927414bf08036482ce7","tid":378241,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T1